data.text: The Spring 2020 issue includes the following articles: - Top of Their Class: Regent’s Annual Scholars Weekend and the launch of a new Honors College this fall attracts the nation’s best and brightest, preparing them to be the next generation of high-caliber Christian leaders. - I Have Walked with The Living God: On the heels of his 90th birthday, Dr. Robertson discusses his latest book project that chronicles his life journey and God’s faithful miracles guiding his every step. - Celebrating 90 Years: Join us in celebrating the 90 th birthday of Regent’s founder and chancellor with a personal greeting or special gift! -Regent World Changer: Meet the hope doctor, Dr. Kelly James (SPC ’11), a licensed professional counselor recently named the Top Mental Health Care Professional for 2019.
